					<div class="ddk33_post_info" post-author="SnowK" post-date="1422529002" post-id="644720" style="display:none;"></div><!--cached-Mon, 05 Jun 2017 16:35:06 +0000--><p>[SnowK, Prisoner-Boratino, Gorv, MadSkeleton. Казнь.]</p>
